data.description: Introducing the desirable Saddle Butte gem in Winchester! This home sits on nearly half an acre, featuring a spacious driveway and a fenced, functional backyard. Inside, you'll find a modern layout with generously high ceilings that flood the space with natural light, creating an open and inviting atmosphere. The kitchen is a true entertainer's delight, boasting ample counter space and a convenient eating bar. The master suite offers a luxurious escape with a shower, soaking tub, and access to a patio. There's also a versatile third bedroom/den and an amazing bonus room. Don't miss out on this exceptional property! Ask about how to save 3 percent on your mortgage interest rate.
